comments.body: Quote from: Alexsurf on March 27, 2023, 05:54:21 AMHello,Does anyone tried to operate S19 series over 90C degree with immersion cooling ?Do you expect any long term damage for a chip at 80-85 C into oil ?Have a good day,why would anyone try 90c when it is not spec?I expect that 79c or lower is better than 80-85-90cWhether you mine in air or oil a bit under top spec is better than over.
